<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { padding: 20px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .amount { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; }
        .status { padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Withdrawal Request Submitted</h2>
        <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
        <p>Your withdrawal request has been successfully submitted.</p>
        <p>Amount: <span class="amount">$<%= amount.toFixed(2) %></span></p>
        <p>Request Date: <%= requestDate %></p>
        <p>Transaction ID: <%= transactionId %></p>
        <p>Your request is pending admin approval. We will notify you once it's processed.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>Mining Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>